                    <span>McTeigue's brilliance is clearly revealed in this book. He has the great ability to help the struggling, mediocre golfer with clear, easy to understand, easy to perform instructions about a typically complicated subject--the effective golf swing. Buy it, read it, you'll see!</span>
                  
              
